# Walkthrough — D365 Live Tracker

## What Was Built

A complete real-time GPS tracking system for Dynamics 365 CRM with Azure Maps visualization, consisting of:

### 📱 Expo Mobile App (`mobile-app/`)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [config.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/constants/config.ts) | Azure AD, D365, location tracking settings, theme colors |
| [types/index.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/types/index.ts) | TypeScript types for all entities |
| [AuthProvider.tsx](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/auth/AuthProvider.tsx) | MSAL auth with SecureStore, silent/interactive token flows |
| [LocationService.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/services/LocationService.ts) | GPS tracking (foreground + background), Haversine distance |
| [D365Client.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/services/D365Client.ts) | D365 Web API client with retry/batch support |
| [TrackingManager.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/services/TrackingManager.ts) | GPS→CRM pipeline with offline queue |
| [useTracking.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/hooks/useTracking.ts) | React hook for tracking state |
| [dashboard.tsx](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/app/(tabs)/dashboard.tsx) | Start/stop tracking, metrics grid, coordinates |
| [history.tsx](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/app/(tabs)/history.tsx) | Past sessions from CRM with details |
| [settings.tsx](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/app/(tabs)/settings.tsx) | Profile, config display, sign-out |
| [login.tsx](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/app/(auth)/login.tsx) | Azure AD login with premium dark UI |

---

### 🗺️ Azure Maps Web Resource (`crm-webresource/`)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [LiveTrackingMap.html](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/crm-webresource/html/LiveTrackingMap.html) | Sidebar + map + metrics overlay layout |
| [LiveTrackingMap.js](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/crm-webresource/js/LiveTrackingMap.js) | Fetches from D365, renders markers + trails, auto-refresh |
| [LiveTrackingMap.css](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/crm-webresource/css/LiveTrackingMap.css) | Dark theme with glassmorphic overlay |

