| MSAL type safety | ✅ **Fixed** — full [MSALAccount](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/node_modules/react-native-msal/build/types.d.ts#124-131) objects, undefined guards |

## Next Steps (for the user)

1. **Configure** — Replace placeholder values in [config.ts](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/mobile-app/src/constants/config.ts) with actual Azure AD & D365 credentials
2. **Create CRM entity** — Follow [docs/crm-entity-setup.md](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/docs/crm-entity-setup.md) to create `rmt_livetracking` entity
3. **Register Azure AD app** — Follow [docs/azure-ad-config.md](file:///d:/Practice/Live%20Tracking%20In%20D365%20Azure%20Map/docs/azure-ad-config.md)
4. **Deploy web resource** — Upload HTML/JS/CSS to D365 as web resources
5. **Test** — Run `npx expo start` and test on a device
